cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.IR, cs.DC, cs.CY

This paper discusses legal issues related to the storage and transmission of video content over the internet, which falls under the category of multimedia (cs.MM). It also covers copyright laws and decisions, which could be classified under cryptography and security (cs.CR) and information retrieval (cs.IR). The technical and economic aspects of video delivery systems are also discussed, which could be related to distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC) and cybernetics (cs.CY).
